The paper deals with natural language processing and sentiment analysis on Twitter data, which are typical topics in the sub-category of Computation and Language (cs.CL). The use of deep learning and attention mechanisms also suggests the sub-category of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also involves classification tasks, which are relevant to the sub-category of Machine Learning (cs.LG). The use of attention mechanisms is also related to the sub-category of Information Retrieval (cs.IR). Finally, the paper deals with social media data, which is relevant to the sub-category of Social and Information Networks (cs.SI).
